Assignment 6 

Problem 3: 
3. A class Time that contains as attributes the hours, the 
minutes, and the seconds and has the following functions: 
a. Properties for all the attributes OR Properties. 
b. Adding two times together and returning a new time object 
correctly.  
c. Resetting a time object by making the hours, minutes and 
seconds equal 0. 
d. Adding a time by 30 minutes and adjusting the hours 
subsequently. 
e. Printing the values of a certain time object. 
f. Convert a given time to a total number of seconds. 
